---
title: Mediterranean Pork & Garlic Almond Crumb with Roast Root Veggie Toss & Capsicum Relish
description: Sure, searing up some plain pork steaks for dinner is all fine and dandy. But why not take it up a notch with this
aromatic herby crumb that's scatted over the pork as a crunchy finishing touch? It'll contrast perfectly with the
tangy pesto dressing. Trust us, this is going to be your new pork dinner.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
